            <title>Google 確認今年內讓 Gemini 全面取代過往推出的 Google Assistant 人工智慧助理服務</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;去年在&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:1;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://mashdigi.com/google-officially-unveiled-the-pixel-9-series-of-phones-including-the-long-exposed-pixel-brands-second-phone-with-a-foldable-screen-the-pixel-9-pro-fold/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:Pixel 9 系列機種;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;Pixel 9 系列機種&lt;/a&gt;推出&lt;span&gt;以 Gemini Anvanced 人工智慧服務驅動的 Gemini Live 服務&lt;/span&gt;時，&lt;a class=&quot;link &quot; href=&quot;https://tw.news.yahoo.com/tag/Google&quot; data-i13n=&quot;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:Google;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0&quot;&gt;Google&lt;/a&gt;便曾暗示原本在 Android 手機提供使用的&lt;span&gt;Google Assistant&lt;/span&gt;數位助理服務，未來將逐漸改以 Gemini 人工智慧數位助理取代。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;caas-figure&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-figure-with-pb&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-img-container caas-img-loader&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;caas-img caas-lazy has-preview&quot; alt=&quot;Google 確認今年內讓 Gemini 全面取代過往推出的 Google Assistant 人工智慧助理服務&quot; src=&quot;https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-03/a7bcfe00-01b3-11f0-bffd-da0aabb925c8&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption class=&quot;caption-collapse&quot;&gt;Google 確認今年內讓 Gemini 全面取代過往推出的 Google Assistant 人工智慧助理服務&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;而在稍早&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:3;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://blog.google/products/gemini/google-assistant-gemini-mobile/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:對外聲明;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;對外聲明&lt;/a&gt;中，Google 確認將開始讓</description>
